window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Coming this summer, the sequel you’ve all b-b-been waiting for....</b></p> <p>Their foothold established, Reach and the soldiers sent to secure Amir have only begun to repair the destruction inflicted on them by hostile neighbors when a terrifying new threat emerges from the deep woods and dark jungles of Amir itself. Something so lethal and evasive, not even Brody can seem to take it down....</p> <p>New threats and old enemies arrive as more mysteries of this new home world are uncovered, and with them, clues to humanity’s own mysterious past.</p> <p><i>Wayward Galaxy 2</i> is the explosive sequel to the blockbuster first book that had sci-fi listeners calling for more. Don’t miss this next installment featuring the gritty combat of Galaxy’s Edge combined with the world-building intrigue of the Renegade Star series performed by award-winning R.C. Bray.</p> <p>Includes a special note from the author.</p>"; 
